Note:
Mobile Overlay Components Module for Mobile UI Framework

This module provides comprehensive overlay components for mobile interfaces.
Includes modal dialogs, bottom sheets, action sheets, popovers, and toast
notifications with mobile-optimized interactions and animations.

Key Features:
- Modal dialogs with various styles
- Bottom sheets and slide-up panels
- Action sheets for contextual actions
- Toast notifications and snackbars
- Popover menus and tooltips
- Alert dialogs and confirmations
- Loading overlays and progress indicators
- Blur effects and backdrop styling
- Gesture-based dismissal
- Keyboard avoidance
- Accessibility compliance
- Platform-specific styling

Provides complete overlay component system for building intuitive mobile
interfaces with proper modal presentations and user feedback.
:End Note

